originalText.text: I had a great experience with the realty company. In search for an apartment, my partner and I were looking all over Westchester County. We contacted Anthony Cipriano on the Sunday before Labor Day, he got back to us immediately, and even gave us a same-day showing. We saw the apartment, and he also gave us the option to view other apartments that he had available in the neighboring town. We fell in love with it and applied ASAP - we heard back the  next business day (Tuesday) with results that we were approved for the apartment we selected. We have since moved in and are in love with our new place. We were in awe as to how helpful and responsive Anthony was, especially on a holiday weekend AND without us having to pay a broker fee! Other brokers that we had dealt with cared more about being paid instead of helping prospective tenants, like us.
